{"tid":1034001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[贏爆廠]  特朗普考慮用行政指令封殺華為","createTime":"2019-02-23T14:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T23:42:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bff52e8bbaca30cbb946ccd5bf268f55456ba99e","tid":1034001,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"President Donald Trump said he may use an executive order to stop Huawei Technologies Co. from selling advanced telecommunications equipment in the U.S.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Well we&rsquo;re not doing anything right now,&rdquo; Trump told reporters when asked about an executive order. &ldquo;So we do that with the attorney general, if we do anything.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-02-22/trump-says-executive-order-to-block-huawei-5g-sales-is-an-option-jsgksyhp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-02-22%2Ftrump-says-executive-order-to-block-huawei-5g-sales-is-an-option-jsgksyhp&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e33d4989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-02-22/trump-says-executive-order-to-block-huawei-5g-sales-is-an-option-jsgksyhp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTrump told reporters at the White House that U.S. officials are not talking about dropping charges against Huawei.<br />\n<br />\nHuawei will be raised with U.S. attorneys and the attorney general in the coming weeks, Trump said, but &ldquo;right now it&rsquo;s not something that we&rsquo;re discussing.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-huawei-tech/trump-says-could-include-huawei-and-zte-in-trade-deal-idUSKCN1QB2EC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-huawei-tech%2Ftrump-says-could-include-huawei-and-zte-in-trade-deal-idUSKCN1QB2EC&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xa3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDB